text:
Good mall and excellent collection of cloths and sports gear.

Finest quality sports shirts start from 10 Ringgets.

Rest of the items also nicely budget priced.

One of my favourite hypermarkets. They are enormous. So many products! You won't find much imported or European goods here, but in terms of local products it is amazing. I love the bath and body section, there is so much variety. Fresh food section is also excellent. Prices are reasonable... budget friendly. There is an ATM machine just outside the entrance which is convenient.
Naz here .. Lunch and then solat .. sambil2 charge RZ450e .. Terbaik Ade port utk charging .. while doing business and charging doesn't feel 15 min take long ..
The best bazaar to refill your kitchen and other groceries. This place got a lot of store and restaurant. Very strategic place for business. Parking is not free. Anyway good place

I wish there were more shops there, but good parking space, and the bazaar Ramadan quite comprehensive.

Will definitely visit again
